obvious.util.Adaptable
public class IvtkTreeMapVis
extends IvtkObviousVisualization

This class is a specialized Obvious visualization for Tree based on the Tree map visualization introduced in the InfoVis Toolkit. This class introduces no new extra parameter to configure the visualization.
